1502
01:47:44.333 --> 01:47:46.210
Yes.

1503
01:47:53.466 --> 01:47:56.429
The next time you come
here, follow the tunnel.

1504
01:47:56.469 --> 01:47:59.140
There are no turns,
so you can't get lost.

1505
01:47:59.181 --> 01:48:00.557
Just keep walking.

1506
01:48:00.599 --> 01:48:02.977
When you get to the end,
you'll be by the river.

1507
01:48:03.018 --> 01:48:05.980
You follow the river
until you get to Mount Ida.

1508
01:48:06.021 --> 01:48:07.773
Why are you telling me this?

1509
01:48:13.362 --> 01:48:14.487
If I die...

1510
01:48:14.529 --> 01:48:15.990
No.

1511
01:48:16.031 --> 01:48:17.866
...I don't know how long
the city will stand.

1512
01:48:17.908 --> 01:48:21.287
If the Greeks get inside
the walls, it's over.

1513
01:48:21.329 --> 01:48:22.955
They'll kill all the men,

1514
