from the city walls...

1515
01:48:24.873 --> 01:48:26.167
Please...

1516
01:48:26.208 --> 01:48:27.668
...and the women
they'll take as slaves.

1517
01:48:27.709 --> 01:48:29.462
And that for you will
be worse than dying.

1518
01:48:29.502 --> 01:48:31.422
