such things?

1519
01:48:31.464 --> 01:48:34.758
Because I want you
to be ready.

1520
01:48:34.800 --> 01:48:36.927
I want you
to get our boy

1521
01:48:36.969 --> 01:48:39.805
and I want you
to bring him here.

1522
01:48:39.847 --> 01:48:42.266
You save as many people
as you can,

1523
01:48:42.308 --> 01:48:44.477
but you get here, and you run.

1524
01:48:51.317 --> 01:48:54.569
I killed a boy today...

1525
01:48:54.611 --> 01:48:57.323
and he was young.

1526
01:48:57.365 --> 01:48:59.867
He was much too young.

1527
